this repository contains the implementation of different kinds of NLP Applications using the hugging face transformers.
1. the first notebook is how to make a custom model using transformers
2. the second notebook is building a question answering pipieline using Qu-An model of the "microsoft/MiniLM-L12-H384-uncased" language model
3. the third notebook is text generation using GPT-2 model
4. the fourth notebook is about text summarization
